  "2204350": {
    "name": "Midnight Heist",
    "steam_appid": 2204350,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204350/extras/fa7b7343895be297454181d8b9649e67.poster.avif?t=1768791246\" width=1000 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204350/extras/fa7b7343895be297454181d8b9649e67.webm?t=1768791246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>从内部摧毁可疑公司</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为 P.E.G.A.S.U.S. 的一员，你秘密地为知名组织执行任务。如果你成功完成了这些任务，你的声望将会提高，你也会被信任，并在此过程中赢得宝贵的奖励。但是，要密切注意是谁雇用了你。这些任务不会没有危险。有传言说，特别是在午夜时分，奇怪的身影会在办公楼里移动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204350/extras/e569179d130bdadc49116ef14bdb2b03.poster.avif?t=1768791246\" width=1000 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204350/extras/e569179d130bdadc49116ef14bdb2b03.webm?t=1768791246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>真正的挑战不是闯入 — 而是熬过今夜</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有传言称，一些非法实验引起了神秘而恐怖的实体的注意。近几年来，这些实体一直在恐吓这座城市，但事情有些不对劲，你必须查明真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204350/extras/af7be3f9ff76088f18d66f9c70d4e96a.poster.avif?t=1768791246\" width=1000 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204350/extras/af7be3f9ff76088f18d66f9c70d4e96a.webm?t=1768791246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>强化你的角色，以承接更艰难的劫案</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>升级你的装备：</strong>通过赚取经验值来解锁和购买更致命的高科技装备</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>提升组织等级：</strong>通过完成他们的任务来获取永久加成</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精通专长：</strong>同时装备并升级最多三个专长，打造你独特的游戏风格</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>制造模块：</strong>使用你偷来的现金。每个随机化的模块都可以极大地增强你的技能或赋予你全新的能力</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204350/extras/20572b9d47f2f5abb8e9a82ebc2f88c8.poster.avif?t=1768791246\" width=1000 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204350/extras/20572b9d47f2f5abb8e9a82ebc2f88c8.webm?t=1768791246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>无限重玩性 — 每次劫案都独一无二</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8张不同大小的地图，结合随机生成的任务，提供了巨大的多样性。每次劫案都会收到随机的主线和支线目标，以及完全随机的战利品和特殊物品。游戏包含6种独特实体，每种实体在外观和技能上都各不相同，使每一局的感觉都截然不同。想要自定义挑战吗？接受黑市任务，来进一步调整你的劫案。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204350/extras/045ccaf73f754cbce0800c5c1ccb0601.poster.avif?t=1768791246\" width=1000 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204350/extras/045ccaf73f754cbce0800c5c1ccb0601.webm?t=1768791246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>黑市是活的，它会影响你的劫案</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在黑市上，你可以出售价值极高的战利品（其价格每天都在变化），并接取黑市任务。这些特殊任务允许你大幅操控你的劫案，以换取更难的挑战来最大化你的战利品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204350/extras/e1b64d08fd7afc8e7a9b220a98e49ab7.poster.avif?t=1768791246\" width=1000 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204350/extras/e1b64d08fd7afc8e7a9b220a98e49ab7.webm?t=1768791246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索午夜之城的故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有两个大型“大行动”战役，总共包含60多个任务，你可以在执行劫案的同时完成它们。每个任务都提供经验值、金钱或你在别处无法获得的特殊皮肤等奖励。每个任务都充满了激动人心的故事情节，将你直接拉入行动的中心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204350/extras/0f1475937443cdc29e0166ca7c6c25f0.poster.avif?t=1768791246\" width=1000 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204350/extras/0f1475937443cdc29e0166ca7c6c25f0.webm?t=1768791246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>不仅如此...</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全球排行榜：</strong>与来自世界各地的玩家竞争</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>死亡后的生机：</strong>当你被抓获但朋友仍然存活时，提供主动游戏玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100多种皮肤：</strong>用于个性化角色定制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>详细统计数据：</strong>追踪你的整个职业生涯和每一项成就</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态天气：</strong>在每张地图上</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏内WIKI：</strong>为新手提供全面的教程</p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 简体中文, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 俄语, 捷克语, 土耳其语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
